snippet.title: Super Mario Nightfall - NSMBFMD Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario Nightfall is a mod of New Super Mario Bros. Wii that will include the following:
- 30+ New levels with a noticable change throughout them!
- Tons of custom tilesets!
- Custom music!
- Custom backgrounds!
- Enemy retextures!
And more!

Gameplay recorded by Swiftshine
Trailer Music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5VCgkuCKElc

Logo made by Miguel
Very special thanks to Rimea for including this trailer in the 2023 NSMB Franchise Modding Direct! https://youtu.be/40OUE8quoz4
